snippet.title: Life With Herpes with Alexandra Harbushka
snippet.description:
Hi my friends!

Welcome to my YouTube channel. If you hit SUBSCRIBE then you are about to learn everything and more about Life With Herpes. Like I always say, "I know this is a community either one of us wanted to be a member of but we are here."  Yes, I have herpes both genital and oral...lucky me. Ok, so here we are so let's have some fun, laugh and learn all we can about this virus. Together we can break the stigma! 

Alright...let's get started and from the bottom of my heart thank you for the opportunity to spend time with you!

xoxo,
Alexandra


If you are ready to learn more and join the community go here :-) https://lifewithherpes.com/
